snippet.title: Cozy Room Decorator - Gameplay Footage (Alpha)
snippet.description:
Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2615130/Cozy_Room_Decorator/

Sign up on our website for more news: https://luckyrollstudio.com/games/cozy-room-decorator

Interested in the alpha or beta? Join our discord: https://discord.com/invite/BHkBQH7Udh

This is alpha footage, we're so excited to share this game with you! The two songs are originals we made just for Cozy Room Decorator!
